Ever Carradine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ever_Carradine 0 Ever Dawn Carradine (born August 6, 1974) is an American actress. She is known for her roles as Tiffany Porter on Once and Again, as Kelly Ludlow on Commander in Chief, and as Naomi Putnam on The Handmaid's Tale.
